headline: Deckers Outdoor (DECK) Launches Teva x Sean Wotherspoon Collection Globally
summary: Deckers Outdoor (DECK) experienced an 8% price increase over the last month, which may have been influenced by several recent developments. Notable was Teva's collaboration with Sean Wotherspoon, launching a limited-edition collection that emphasized both vintage and modern design, including the reimagined Wraptor shoe and Hurricane XLT2. Additionally, HOKA's Mafate 5 launch for ultra-runners showcased advanced technology, potentially boosting interest in the brand. While the broader market...

headline: Teva® and Sean Wotherspoon Reimagine Archival Icons, Bridging Street Style and Outdoor Adventure
summary: GOLETA, Calif., August 14, 2025--Teva styles reimagined with Sean Wotherspoon’s signature palette, spirit, and vintage flair.
